Apocalypse saw the triple attack on hell beast. He watched as the bot death 
tried to put the spear through his back. he jettesend towards aracnia and 
landed infront of her at the same time the new bot in the pure liquid metal 
form attacked hell beast and death attempted to slit aracnia's throat. He 
took his sword and drove it at her spark center. He turned in the corner of 
his eye and watched as war came from hell beats's right side about 10 feet 
from him and shot multiple wrist shots at his side. Famine came at hell 
beasts legs and tried to drive the needle in his finger in his cafe muscel. 
It would nock him out cold if it entered him. Peastlense took his blade and 
joined in on the attack and tried to drive his sword through the bots back.
